    {
      "id": 1773336577208,
      "title": "Postal FEP Pacific",
      "content": "For FEP Pacific customers: update to Blue Shield FEP if the claim has an initial 25 claim number, an R policy, and California state.&nbsp;<div>Reference: <a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/message/19:040d113871eb4d6bab8685db63548e85@thread.v2/1773336320971?context=%7B%22contextType%22%3A%22chat%22%7D\" target=\"_blank\">Link</a></div>",
