      "updatedAt": "3/26/2026, 4:03:18 PM",
      "updatedBy": "Jasfer B.",
      "visibility": [
        "articles"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 1773323657893,
      "title": "FEP or FEDERAL FEP",
      "content": "Always make queries with the POC even if instructions exist from the payor mapping team on how to identify an FEP claim.&nbsp;<div>Reference: <a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/message/19:8896d4bb6d414e79abe25a27824352c0@thread.v2/1773156912893?context=%7B%22contextType%22%3A%22chat%22%7D\" target=\"_blank\">Link</a></div>",
